    <rigor-reason>Multi-FR composite (FR-18, FR-19, FR-21) touching the widget registry + the canonical ContextPaneController. Wires the load-bearing PaneEventBus `workspace` channel dispatch path â€” getting widget_type values wrong breaks all 7 GetStarted cards. Modifies the same file as task 040 (must serialize). Registry change has cross-cutting impact: PlaybookGalleryWidget MUST remain resolvable for non-welcome stages.</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>D</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>false</parallel-safe>
